            HP₀ = <strong>${fmt(sun0.hp,6)}°</strong></p>
            <p>Zenith₀ = 90 + 34/60 + 9/3600 + SD₀ - HP₀ + dip = <strong>${fmt(zenith0)}°</strong></p>
            
