        <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Plug into the formula.</p>
        <div style="font-family: monospace; white-space: normal; word-break: break-word; margin: 10px 0;">
            <p>sin(alt) = ${sinLat.toFixed(6)} × ${sinDec.toFixed(6)} + ${cosLat.toFixed(6)} × ${cosDec.toFixed(6)} × ${cosLHA.toFixed(6)}</p>
            <p>= ${(sinLat * sinDec).toFixed(6)} + ${(cosLat * cosDec * cosLHA).toFixed(6)}</p>
