    if (eot > 12) eot -= 24;
    if (eot < -12) eot += 24;
    
    return `
        <p><span class="formula">Moon's Equation of Time (EOT)</span></p>
        <p>EOT for the Moon is the difference between apparent lunar time and mean lunar time.</p>
