        <p>ΔT = <span class="value">${dt.toFixed(2)} sec</span></p>
        <hr>
        <p><span class="formula">Formula:</span> EOT = -local_hour + GHA/15 + 12 (normalized to ±12).</p>
        <p>local_hour = fractional part of JD × 24 = <span class="value">${localHour.toFixed(4)} h</span></p>
        <p>GHA = <span class="value">${formatDMS(moonData.gha)}</span> → GHA/15 = <span class="value">${(moonData.gha/15).toFixed(4)} h</span></p>
        <p>EOT = -${localHour.toFixed(4)} + ${(moonData.gha/15).toFixed(4)} + 12 = <span class="value">${eot.toFixed(4)} h</span></p>
        <p><span class="formula">Final Moon EOT:</span> <strong>${formatTimePrecise(eot)}</strong></p>
    `;
